{"tid":1950210,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"屎忽痕想記錄低自己食過嘅黃店（非批鬥）","createTime":"2020-03-30T07:46:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-10T14:59:57.000Z","uid":34147,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"24f92f212cb4dca7931b2404c45a1705fc86f9ee","tid":1950210,"uid":34147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T07:46:13.000Z","msg":"先此聲明，下面會有讚有彈，但唔是批鬥post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 只屬個人意見，非專業食評，大家睇完下就算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n分數方面會係1-10分：<br />\n1分係貼錢都唔食，<br />\n5分係中規中矩，無咩特別事都未必會再食，<br />\n10分係比市價貴、路遠都照食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KuVVonE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKuVVonE.png&h=17049e84&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第一間打頭陣嘅係best of the best<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 已經食咗四、五次嘅<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">金撈</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">9/10</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n1. 食開佢個花膠雞湯底，有一塊大花膠，半隻雞，次次都飲返三碗先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2. 炸魚皮脆卜卜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n3. 烏冬中規中矩<br />\n4. 安格斯牛，肥瘦比大概2:8 / 3:7，鍾意食偏瘦嘅一流<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n5. 菠蘿雪芭，新鮮菠蘿即叫即整<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n6. 生菜，中規中矩，但因為個湯好撚正我又特別鍾意生菜，所以次次都會j <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n7. 蝦滑本人好好食，但上面有啲疑似魚子（？）嘅嘢失咗少少分。<br />\n8. 竹蔗茅根同檸檬薏米水，好足料足味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n黃店部份唔打啦，廢事又批鬥唔夠黃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n總結：so far 食過咁多次，無一樣食材係below average，全部都係中間以上，加上個湯實在太出色，畀到<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">9/10</span></span></strong>。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n價錢方面好睇嗰日嗌咗咩，兩個人就HKD$600左右落樓，有次屎忽痕嗌咗貴嘢就HKD$900<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唯一最大缺點係唔就腳，九成九搭巴士都要轉車，一係就佐敦彌敦道行20分鐘。<br />\n<br />\n順帶一提，星期六去食嗰陣成晚得兩枱客，聽到佢哋員工傾偈都話生意好差，大家幫到手嘅可以去食下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢有隔枱座、量體溫同畀搓手液洗手㗎～<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n名：金撈老鴨湯<br />\n地址：佐敦文昌街文昌樓地下<br />\n電話：2332 7600<br />\n時間：google 寫就3pm-2am，但個人經驗之談就3pm-11pm 最穩陣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efa9215d6724579054e9d53f7f4fb542850c8352","tid":1950210,"uid":34147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T07:49:40.000Z","msg":"google 偷嘅圖，出處可以睇返張圖個user<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1eyG3xH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1eyG3xH.png&h=797146ee&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"03655892bb314dade4c3aa8b40d18c469791bb99","tid":1950210,"uid":124340,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T07:56:25.000Z","msg":"舊花膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但學生哥食唔起 睇吓圖當食咗算<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23781a2f32dedca1e3cbd96e1c03a63fcd2ee495","tid":1950210,"uid":32063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T08:16:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"96e014fa741039b9f2fa7ce534351f9726e1001e","tid":1950210,"uid":34147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T08:27:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eamxqYH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeamxqYH.png&h=3c2640da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n再嚟第二間係好出名嘅<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>616</strong></span></span>，但我只係畀到<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">5/10</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"6b82907cb61da5b83d2f14ead9289e1951829382","tid":1950210,"uid":34147,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T08:31:22.000Z","msg":"（續）<br />\n其實佢啲嘢唔係差，但又未至於好食到要返轉頭，所以根據我嘅評分準則就跌到落5/10<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n嗰次嗌咗兩款牛（成四五個月前，已經唔記得邊兩款），可能係因為我哋唔識淥，食落都有啲韌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 個湯無特別、烏冬無特別、生菜無特別... 所以成件事就係無特別<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"023b37d8e262bbc53ff12b8b73c9eb9d4ad4b387","tid":1950210,"uid":34147,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T08:34:32.000Z","msg":"（續）<br />\n睇過其他post，有啲手足話鍾意食牛嘅，嗌到好多唔同部位試好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 如果大家鍾意食牛嘅，都不防一試。呢間嘢一向都黃到金，好出名，又有幾間分店，點都有一間就腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n因為懶我就唔一間一間打哂啲詳細電話地址出嚟，請大家多啲click 下和你eat<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PmRmjkT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPmRmjkT.png&h=c468a42b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a9a28bba5bf429a5d397663cc6405e0f357d41b7","tid":1950210,"uid":34147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T14:51:03.000Z","msg":"第三間推介嘅黃店係<strong> <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">抬摃 </span><span style=\"color: gold;\">7/10</span></span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/pg/%E6%8A%AC%E6%91%83-2020070784966977/posts/?ref=page_internal\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fpg%2F%25E6%258A%25AC%25E6%2591%2583-2020070784966977%2Fposts%2F%3Fref%3Dpage_internal&d=HeGJypC3zV9uypmZg8TJ2cWiAETkOtN%2FvKUl8N5Dwlc%3D&h=e421e21e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/pg/%E6%8A%AC%E6%91%83-2020070784966977/posts/?ref=page_internal</a><br />\n地點：大角咀博文街4號地下 (台灣餐廳)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VVnuunN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVVnuunN.jpg&h=d5d859cd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2rrZRAC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2rrZRAC.jpg&h=44d4e3fa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n1. 肉燥飯無得輸，多肉燥﹑珍珠米，仲要彈牙唔會煲太耐冧哂。8/10<br />\n2. 我本身鍾意食台式香腸，佢嘅腸都做到幾台灣口味。8/10<br />\n3. 鹽酥雞，好普通，但好在唔會炸到她乾i或者完全無味得味粉，都有 6/10<br />\n4. 紅燒牛肉麵，佢個湯底好甜所以好個人。我本身鍾意食甜就鍾意到不得了，但有朋友唔鍾意食甜覺得畀我伏咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 7/10<br />\n5. 珍珠奶茶，熱同凍都好好飲！一樣，珍珠唔會煲到好冧，嗌少甜就啱啱好！7/10<br />\n6. 關冬煮烏冬，應該係我試過最伏嘅 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 個關冬煮好似餸頭餸尾，個烏冬就合格，但比個餸拉低哂啲分 SAD 5/10<br />\n7. 鹽酥雞翼，同上面鹽酥雞一樣：普通，唔會炸到好乾i或者完全無味得味粉，都有 6/10<br />\n<br />\n另外有兩點要留意返：<br />\n** 上面嗰張罷工CAP圖喺上年CAP嘅，而家已經搵唔返個POST。最近去都好似換咗老闆，大家自己判斷食唔食。<br />\n** 間嘢告急咗一段時間，而家會做埋外賣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"654ea8881e620f59c6a7c6b19260292c48ab361c","tid":1950210,"uid":34147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T14:59:57.000Z","msg":"再嚟都係一間小店，<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">京典</span>，<span style=\"color: gold;\">7/10</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uJSm404.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuJSm404.jpg&h=22ab72a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢間好唔準，因為只係試過一次，但個感受唔錯。<br />\n1. 豬軟骨，超冧，又夠入味 7/10<br />\n2. 麵，好正常嘅上海麵，我本身唔好上海麵，所以呢部份低分啲 5/10<br />\n3. 湯底，都幾足料，又蕃茄又椰菜，無乜味精！7/10<br />\n<br />\n缺點：<br />\n可能因為無乜生意，嗰日去買直頭無炒嘢﹙講緊係食飯時間7PM左右﹚，豆漿又無﹑菜蜜又無 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 全場仲要得一個客，連埋我都得兩個外賣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 希望近坑口嘅朋友仔如果買外賣可以考慮下佢，坑口本身已經少黃店，唔可以畀佢消失呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}